{"tid":1017501,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C.朗遭遇重擊 母親乳腺癌復發","createTime":"2019-02-11T13:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T10:12:48.000Z","uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"28ed65879b4cc2b24ec032ea18dcb0f71af12d8e","tid":1017501,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2019/02/11/4/4f95191cdda9f22e5a58e9bbdfbc6a22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2019%2F02%2F11%2F4%2F4f95191cdda9f22e5a58e9bbdfbc6a22.jpg&h=f084364d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　　C.朗拿度的母親多洛雷斯2007年被診斷患有乳腺癌，她通過手術移除了右側乳房的腫塊，頑強地戰勝了病魔。但本週四64歲的多洛雷斯對葡萄牙媒體透露，她的癌症復發，並在不久前接受了另一次手術，目前正在服用抗癌藥物控制病情。<br />\n<br />\n　　多洛雷斯說道：「我在馬德里做了左側乳房的手術，我接受了放療，現在我正在為自己的生命而戰。」但多洛雷斯並沒有透露手術的具體時間：「沒有人知道我做了第二次手術。」<br />\n<br />\n　　值得一提的是，2007年多洛雷斯接受手術之後，C.朗拿度曾為醫院捐款10萬英鎊，感謝這家醫療機構拯救了母親的生命。"},{"pid":"4ddbcf6309c20d05e6bed67558a71b44e6f6e326","tid":1017501,"uid":1354,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"報係老母身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee537c55ef96caabf3b2a1e04749a95344beab9","tid":1017501,"uid":20634,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"4ddbcf6309c20d05e6bed67558a71b44e6f6e326","tid":1017501,"uid":1354,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"報係老母身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:15:51.000Z","msg":"基斯坦奴朗拿度母親高調力挺兒子，相信他並沒有強姦美國女子Kathryn Mayorga。 2019/02/07<br />\n<br />\nC.朗遭遇重擊！母親乳腺癌復發 2019-02-11"},{"pid":"5389fab4e13f9162f832c74833f21075beee10a9","tid":1017501,"uid":165817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ddbcf6309c20d05e6bed67558a71b44e6f6e326","tid":1017501,"uid":1354,"like":4,"dislike":22,"score":-18,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T13:14:27.000Z","msg":"報係老母身上<img src=\"/assets/faces/